title: All Too Well: The Short Film (10 Minute Version) (Taylor's Version)
description:
It's been an incredible week for Swifties, and we have a lot to discuss. We were not only blessed with the 10 minute version of All Too Well, Taylor directed a short film as well. Sadie Sink and Dylan O'Brien broke our hearts all over again. Ana, Lacey, Amy and Nick break down the new lyrics, the video, the Easter eggs and the intent behind this short film!
What did we miss? What would you like next? Let us know!
